SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT BADT.BADT_HANDLINGDATE, cast(sum (BADT.BADT_NPAYMENTS) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(BADT.BADT_DEBITSCURRH) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum (BADT.BADT_CREDITSCURRH) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum (BADT.BADT_MUTDAILYSTATEMENTS) as decimal(13,2)), count(*) as NUMBER_OF_ACOUNT_STATEMENTS FROM :1/BADT AS BADT, :1/ADMU AS ADMU WHERE BADT.BADT_HANDLINGDATE BETWEEN ':2' and ':3'and BADT.BADT_BANK_ADMNO = ADMU.ADMU_ADMNO and ADMU_ALLOW_QUERY_BANK = 'Y' and ADMU_HUSR_ID = ':4' GROUP BY BADT.BADT_HANDLINGDATE ORDER BY BADT.BADT_HANDLINGDATE FOR FETCH ONLY

SELECT BADT.BADT_HANDLINGDATE,cast(sum (BADT.BADT_NPAYMENTS) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(BADT.BADT_DEBITSCURRH) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum (BADT.BADT_CREDITSCURRH) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum (BADT.BADT_MUTDAILYSTATEMENTS) as decimal(13,2)),count(*) as NUMBER_OF_ACOUNT_STATEMENTS FROM :1/BADT AS BADT WHERE BADT.BADT_HANDLINGDATE BETWEEN ':2' and ':3' GROUP BY BADT.BADT_HANDLINGDATE ORDER BY BADT.BADT_HANDLINGDATE
